The '''Chalactan Enlightenment''' was the highest spirutual attainment of the [[Chalactan Adepts/Legends|Chalactan Adepts]]. Those who achieved it wore the [[Greater Mark of Illumination]]. The Enlightenment was symbolized by the [[Uncloseable Eye]].

